He likes it here.
He's making progress.

566
00:27:47,458 --> 00:27:49,251
Okay, he lost his cool.

567
00:27:49,251 --> 00:27:51,086
But I don't think
that'll happen again.

568
00:27:51,086 --> 00:27:54,131
Vic, he can't hide
in here forever.

569
00:27:54,131 --> 00:27:56,634
He has to face reality sometime.

570
00:27:56,634 --> 00:27:58,552
The kid's had too much
reality lately

571
00:27:58,552 --> 00:27:59,761
