is a latinum mine

596
00:28:40,886 --> 00:28:42,095
and you don't
even know it.

597
00:28:42,095 --> 00:28:43,722
In my opinion

598
00:28:43,722 --> 00:28:45,599
it's time to expand
the business.

599
00:28:45,599 --> 00:28:48,477
Nog, this is
a holosuite.

600
00:28:48,477 --> 00:28:50,145
Of course
it's a holosuite.

601
00:28:50,145 --> 00:28:54,483
But that doesn't mean
we can't build a new casino.

602
00:28:54,483 --> 00:28:56,443
A new casino?

603
00:28:56,443 --> 00:28:58,362
How much money do I have?

604
00:28:58,362 --> 00:29:00,364
If you'll excuse us,
Counselor.

