00:31:11,870 --> 00:31:12,830
Good evening.

641
00:31:12,830 --> 00:31:14,247
I'll take care
of them.

642
00:31:14,247 --> 00:31:15,624
Hey, long time
no see.

643
00:31:15,624 --> 00:31:17,334
Oh, Nog.

644
00:31:19,712 --> 00:31:21,588
Right this way.

645
00:31:21,588 --> 00:31:26,426
(<i> band plays instrumental</i>
