all the profits.

651
00:31:39,732 --> 00:31:42,401
Those are holographic
profits, right?

652
00:31:42,401 --> 00:31:43,943
Yeah.

653
00:31:43,943 --> 00:31:46,071
So, what's new with you?

654
00:31:46,071 --> 00:31:47,947
Well...

655
00:31:47,947 --> 00:31:50,242
Rom got a promotion.

656
