threw him a party last night.

664
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:08,260
Oh.

665
00:32:08,260 --> 00:32:09,887
LEETA:
It was a spur-of-
the-moment thing.

666
00:32:09,887 --> 00:32:12,097
No invitations or anything.

667
00:32:12,097 --> 00:32:13,682
Don't worry about it.

668
00:32:13,682 --> 00:32:15,308
